name: Barbeque Glazed Meatballs
author: Anonymous
summary: Sooooo irresistible! These easy meatballs, jazzed up a two-ingredient glaze, could well become your own 'most-requested' signature party dish.
ingredients: 1 (16 ounce) bottle barbecue sauce, any flavor
1 (28 ounce) package Market Pantry™ frozen fully cooked homestyle meatballs
directions: Place barbecue sauce and jelly in slow cooker
Cover and heat on High 10  minutes, or until hot
Heat meatballs in microwave as directed on package
Add meatballs to sauce and stir gently to coat
Reduce heat to Low to keep warm while serving
